{
  "stem": "1858.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I would have loved to have-- after I wrote the letter-- to have heard from him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I don't know if maybe he didn't live there anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Maybe he didn't survive himself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "But anyway, end of the war, we were working, as I said, in fields.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And one day, the head of the Gestapo in our camp-- we called him [NON-ENGLISH], that was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "He came into the field and he called-- there were seven girls my age.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "We were the youngest.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "He called us and gathered us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And he told us, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Come with me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And he took us away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And my sisters were working in the field that day, were watching as I was being led away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And he was a terribly brutal man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "If a girl would do anything, he could just throw her on the floor, step on her neck, choke her.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "He was a beast.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the girls looked at us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What are they going to do with those children?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where are they taking them?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My sister started to cry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he led us to a different field and then he told us to run.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as we started running, the seven of us, we thought, he's going to shoot us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, suddenly, he told us, halt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And just like nothing, he told us, I want you to pick the flowers in the field.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "First we thought, we don't hear right, or we are crazy, or is he crazy?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We picked the flowers, and we brought it to him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he started laughing at us because he saw that fear.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We did not know what he was doing to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then he chased us in the field some more.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He made us run like-- as though we were horses and he was just chasing us.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
